

Requirements
============

- Windows XP/Vista/7 32 bit
- Visual Studio 2008/2010


Compilation with VS 2008
========================

- add the framework's include folder in Tools -> Options -> Projects and Solutions -> VC++ Directories -> Include
- open code/vs/DummyFramework_VCXX
- click Rebuild Solution
- open projects/Projects_VCXX
- similarly Rebuild Solution

Compilation with VS 2010
========================

- same as above, but no need to set directories



